  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "She's been around for roughly 50 years, and Wendy the Good Little Witch finally has her own handheld video game. The laws of gravity have been upset, and Wendy is to blame! Help her trek through level after level of maddening obstacles and deadly enemies in order to set things right. There are hidden Moon Stones that Wendy must find in order to get things back to normal, but they're spread out over four vast levels of harrowing action. Packed with strange locations and tough mysteries to solves, WENDY: Every Witch Way features four bonus levels hat have you earning points by flying through the air on a broom, avoiding flying objects, and taking out would-be deterrents with a magic wand. Boasting detailed, cartoon-style graphics and some of the most original gameplay you've ever laid eyes on, WENDY: Every Witch Way is a truly magical experience for gamers of all ages.",
